  "content": {
    "problemStatement": "### **Aptitude Practice Question**\n\nGiven a constant k, such that k:5 is proportional to 10:25. Find the value of k.\n\n---\n\n### **Answer & Explanation**\n\nSince k:5 is proportional to 10:25, we can write,\n\nk / 5 = 10 / 25\nk = 10/25 \u00d7 5 = 2\n\nSo, the value of k is 2.",
